[I] Educational Programming Environment

[T] KTurtle is an educational programming environment for learning how to
[T] program. It provides all programming tools from its user interface. The
[T] programming language used is TurtleScript, which is loosely based on Logo.

[U] https://apps.kde.org/kturtle/

